            <span class="section-tag">Our Story</span>
            <h2>Born From a Real Need</h2>
            <p>Work & Study Beyond Borders was founded with one burning question in mind — why do so many talented Nigerians get turned away, exploited by fake agents, or simply give up on their dream of going abroad?</p>
            <p>We built WSBB to change that. Based in Enugu and serving clients across Nigeria and West Africa, we offer honest, end-to-end guidance that takes you from "I want to go abroad" all the way to landing on foreign soil with a clear plan.</p>
            <p>No hidden fees. No false promises. Just real support from people who genuinely care about your future.</p>
